Source: Supplied.Earlier this year, the bank was also recognised by Brand Finance as the second strongest banking brand in the world.Francois Viviers, executive of marketing and communications at Capitec, says, “It’s fantastic to see the Capitec brand recognised as the strongest brand in SA. "We were agile in our response to the challenges Covid-19 imposed, and we used the pandemic as an opportunity to respond with innovations in digital banking that help our clients bank better. "The Brand Finance result just confirms that our relentless focus on the needs of our clients is the driving force behind the Capitec movement.”